  "intro": "<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Early start from Cuba</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>I was trying to go 120 miles to Grants, NM and therefore I was on the road before 6am. I also was trying to\n\t\t\t\t\t\tget my miles in before the afternoon winds and rain picked up. There was a nice sunrise at my back.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic01.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"talk to text-muted\">Sunrise over Cuba at about 6am\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>",
  "prevDay": 31,
  "nextDay": 33,
  "content": "<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic02.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">A rainbow was trying to break through.\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Heading into the rain</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel1\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic04.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                          class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Behind me it was sunny</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic03.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Up ahead there were rainbows</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic05.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>But also some clouds</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic06.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                   class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>The clouds delivered an early shower</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tOnce I got through an hour or so of rain the land leveled out.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic07.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">It was hard to tell what the terrain ahead was going to deliver</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Some canyons all around so the road continued to roll up and down. By 8:30 in the morning I reached the\n\t\t\t\t\t\tlast spot for supplies and went in for coffee. I hadn't used up much of my gatorade so there was no need to\n\t\t\t\t\t\tbuy more. The rain had kept the temperature down.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel2\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel2\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic08.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>After the first rain</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic09.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>wide open spaces</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic10.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>on all sides</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic11.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>I crossed the continental divide 4 times during the day but barely noticed since the entire area was so\n\t\t\t\t\t\tflat there was very little differentiating one rise from another.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel3\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic12.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Looking north</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic13.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Looking south</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic14.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>West - The road goes on forever</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic15.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>West - The road goes on forever</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe first 50 miles was heading west and I was hoping that I would turn south before the wind picked up\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic17.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tNo big hills - Just steep enough to make you stand and push over the hump and then get a bit of a downhill.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic18.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Wide open spaces</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic19.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tCouldnt always tell what was ahead but knew it was going to be a long day\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic20.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">Not much more to say\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"section-heading\">Rolling up thru desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tA change in the terrain once I was heading south I was also gradually climbing.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel4\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel4\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic21.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n                                                                  class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>A break from the flat</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic23.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>A break from the flat</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic24.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>A break from the flat</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic25.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n                                                           class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>A break from the flat</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel4\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel4\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThere was a 25 mile section which was generally rolling up and occasionally had sections that were pretty\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsteep.\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic26.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tA couple of these came after the 80 mile mark and after I had put on my rain gear and then taken it off a\n\t\t\t\t\t\tcouple times.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic27.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI didn't realize how close to the top I was when I flagged down a white pickup and he actually stopped.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic21.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"section-heading\">Heading down into the New Mexico's July tsunami</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day32/day32pic35.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"caption text-muted\">My ride down into Grants\n                                    </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThis guy picked me up and we put my bike in the back of his truck for the final 28 miles into Milan, NM.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWe had a nice talk and I avoided the thunderstorms and other weather that seemed imminent at the time.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBy the tume\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twe reached Milan the sun was out and it was a beautiful afternoon.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Once he dropped me off at the truck stop in Milan I still had 4 miles to go. It was a nice time of day and\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI stopped to dry my stuff out, talked to my wife and got something to eat. Before I knew it a huge storm was\n\t\t\t\t\t\tblowing in from the exact direction I needed to go. The next four miles were as tough as any on the trip. I\n\t\t\t\t\t\twas going down hill into Grants and pedaling as hard as I could into a 25-30 mph wind. The rain started\n\t\t\t\t\t\tduring the last one-half mile before I arrived at the Grant's Comfort Inn.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The wind continued to blow until later in the evening. In the morning there really wasn't much wind. It\n\t\t\t\t\t\twould switch back on about noon each day from here on out.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Text by <a href=\"http://www.havingadventures.com/\">Jim O'Brien</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t. Photographs by Jim O'Brien<a href=\"https://flic.kr/s/aHsk9CwBC1\">TD on Flickr</a>.</p>"
}